bool IDAC_Init_TypeDef::prsEnable

Enable Peripheral reflex system (PRS) to control IDAC output. If false, the IDAC output is controlled by writing to IDAC_OUTEN in IDAC_CTRL or by calling IDAC_OutEnable().
